    "body" : "There is nothing else.  <code>PATH</code> should be all you need to make <code>java -version</code> work.  So check that your update to <code>PATH</code> is correct.  What happens when you run <code>C:\\Program Files\\Java\\jdk-17\\bin\\java -version</code> ?"
